[{"id": 18823504383891, "url": "https://optisignshelp.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/18823504383891.json", "html_url": "https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/18823504383891-OptiSigns-Getting-Started-Guide", "author_id": 373132830174, "comments_disabled": true, "draft": false, "promoted": true, "position": 0, "vote_sum": -5, "vote_count": 41, "section_id": 26398357451923, "created_at": "2023-07-24T04:12:27Z", "updated_at": "2025-02-25T21:23:03Z", "name": "OptiSigns - Getting Started Guide", "title": "OptiSigns - Getting Started Guide", "source_locale": "en-us", "locale": "en-us", "outdated": false, "outdated_locales": [], "edited_at": "2025-02-25T21:23:02Z", "user_segment_id": null, "permission_group_id": 787493, "content_tag_ids": [], "label_names": ["screen"], "body": "<h2 id=\"h_01HWQRE4G5M1F6W6G6SQ0M6PKG\">New to OptiSigns or need a refresher? Here's your one-stop guide to get your screens ready to go!</h2>\n<h4 id=\"h_01HWR0AEX2REG6PW8CJ24XEG0P\">In this article:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#Set\">Set Up Your Hardware</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#Upload\">Upload Your Content</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#Push\">Push Content to Your Screen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#Helpful\">Helpful Information</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a name=\"Set\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HWQRF8KY97SVZE2VG1YXXATR\">Set Up Your Hardware</h2>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 58.3278%;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\">We recommend watching our short how-to video so you get to know the basics. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 id=\"h_01HYK72XKBGBSFWR0K5W8NR590\"><iframe src=\"//www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/s-vxhAu5jTU\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></h4>\n<h4 id=\"h_01HYK72XKBHB2TFBZZ01CSAPZW\">Pick one of the 3 ways below to get OptiSigns running on your TV:</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>The easiest way to get started is to get your favorite brand of TV and get our<strong> <a href=\"https://shop.optisigns.com/products/optisigns-android-stick-player-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OptiSigns Android Digital Signage Player</a></strong> to run OptiSigns on it. Follow <strong><a href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/27267311796243\">this guide</a></strong> to learn how to set up your OptiSigns Player</li>\n<li>Already have a TV or Signage Player? Go to our<strong> <a href=\"https://www.optisigns.com/download\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Downloads</a></strong> page to see if our app can be installed on it.</li>\n<li>Not ready for hardware purchase yet? Just download the <strong><a href=\"https://links.optisigns.com/win\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Windows Player app</a></strong> or <strong><a href=\"https://links.optisigns.com/mac\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">MacOS Player app</a></strong> and use your laptop as test screen.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Once OptiSigns App is installed, <strong>launch it</strong>. </p>\n<p>The app will ask if you want to automatically start when the device starts up.</p>\n<p>Then, you will see this <strong>pairing screen:</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/29654073549587\" alt=\"OptiSigns_Digital_Signage_wKluheZldi_1_960x540.png\"></p>\n<p>Go to the OptiSigns portal: <a href=\"https://app.optisigns.com/\">https://app.optisigns.com/</a></p>\n<p>Once logged in, click <strong>Add Screen.</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/29654049959443\"></p>\n<p>A pop-up screen will appear, type in the <strong>Pair Code</strong> showing up on your screen. Then, click <strong>Pair</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/29654073598099\"></p>\n<p>Your screen should now say <strong>Paired</strong>, instead of showing the code.</p>\n<p><a name=\"Upload\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HWQSX99N8M87Q6JPHCEMXB6S\"><strong>Upload Your Content</strong></h2>\n<p>Go to <strong><a href=\"https://app.optisigns.com/app/assetManagement\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Files/Assets</a></strong> page</p>\n<p>Click <strong>Upload Files.</strong></p>\n<p>Then <strong>drop</strong>, <strong>import</strong>, or <strong>browse</strong> for files to upload to your account.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/29654073621267\"></p>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 72.8554%;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><strong>Note</strong></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\">We support Images, Videos, PowerPoint, etc. Click <a href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016342373\">here</a> for more detailed information on the files we support.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 id=\"h_01HYK72XKBVFG2VXZVQSWVJ33S\">You can also learn more ways to customize your screens with these guides:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/28295104605843\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">How to Create and Use Playlists:</a></strong> If you'd like to have a series of rotating content on your screen</li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360026559573\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">How to Create Split Screens Layout: </a></strong>If you want to split your screen into zones to show different content.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a name=\"Push\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HWQYPS8NTC81K99KRMB0WBW6\"><strong>Push Content to Your Screen</strong></h2>\n<p>Go back to the <strong>Screens </strong>page, and click <strong>Edit </strong>on your preferred screen.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/29654073649043\"></p>\n<p>For <strong>Type</strong>, select your desired content: asset, playlist or schedule. For this example, we chose a <strong>Playlist.</strong></p>\n<p>Then, select your desired content from the drop down menu.</p>\n<p>Finally, click <strong>Save</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/29654050066067\"></p>\n<p><a name=\"Helpful\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HXCVA1S881K995E3VWEYXFE1\"><strong>Helpful Information</strong></h2>\n<p>Now that your screens are set up and ready to go, here are some additional guides and information to take your screens to the next level:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Explore thousands of templates: <a href=\"https://canvas.optisigns.com/templates/search/birthday\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">birthdays</a>, <a href=\"https://canvas.optisigns.com/templates/category/Holidays%20and%20Observances\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">holidays</a>, <a href=\"https://canvas.optisigns.com/templates/search/anniversary\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">anniversaries</a>, <a href=\"https://canvas.optisigns.com/templates/search/announcement\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">announcements</a>, etc.</li>\n<li>Build your own <a href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360017964153\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Weather app.</a>\n</li>\n<li>Make a <a href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360026559573\">Split Screen app.</a>\n</li>\n<li>Automate your screen with <a href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016981853\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Schedules </a>or use the <a href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360042736794\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Live &amp; Expire</a> feature.</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016990233\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Invite a team member</a> to help you manage your screens.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HWQYXTN37H6D4WE20RC6JZRQ\"><strong>That's it!</strong></h2>"}, {"id": 25607930101907, "url": "https://optisignshelp.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/25607930101907.json", "html_url": "https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/25607930101907-How-to-get-the-most-out-of-your-Digital-Signs", "author_id": 373132830174, "comments_disabled": true, "draft": false, "promoted": false, "position": 1, "vote_sum": 4, "vote_count": 6, "section_id": 26398357451923, "created_at": "2024-01-26T20:44:53Z", "updated_at": "2024-11-21T22:27:32Z", "name": "How to get the most out of your Digital Signs", "title": "How to get the most out of your Digital Signs", "source_locale": "en-us", "locale": "en-us", "outdated": false, "outdated_locales": [], "edited_at": "2024-06-04T19:03:31Z", "user_segment_id": null, "permission_group_id": 787493, "content_tag_ids": [], "label_names": [], "body": "<p id=\"h_01HN3RAHG7P6FPXAJ0GEM555E7\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\" style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 21px;\">Here is a quick list of ideas and things you can achieve with OptiSigns to get the most out of your digital signs:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 21px;\">Beside images, videos you can also upload any <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016342373-What-types-of-files-are-supported\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">PDF, PowerPoint, and many other file types</a></span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 21px;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/25127398699667-How-to-add-a-QR-Code-in-designs-using-OptiSigns-Canvas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Add QR Codes</a> to your screens</span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 21px;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/20425113117459\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Use our Templates</a> to save your time creating content</span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 21px;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/18988049363859-Push-Contents-to-your-Screens\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Use Push to Screens</a> feature to easily schedule content changes or temporary take over</span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 21px;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360016981853-Create-and-using-Schedules-with-OptiSigns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Use Schedules</a> or <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360042736794\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Live &amp; Expire</a> for more scheduling options</span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 21px;\">OptiSigns integrate easily with your existing tools: <a class=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360050642833-How-to-use-Google-Slides-with-OptiSigns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Google Slides</a>, <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360019517953-How-to-use-Google-Calendar-with-OptiSigns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Calendar</a>, <a class=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/1500005888781-How-to-use-Canva-designs-with-OptiSigns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Canva</a>, <a class=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360024859713-How-to-use-Microsoft-PowerBI-Dashboard-Report-with-OptiSigns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">PowerBI</a>, and <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://www.optisigns.com/apps\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">more</a></span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 21px;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://feeds.optisigns.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Explore our Feeds</a>, it's curated, prebuilt fresh content for your screens.</span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 21px;\">If you are looking to add more screens, you can <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://app.optisigns.com/app/s/android-devices\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">order Pre-Configured Devices</a> from us. They'll ship directly to your locations and save you time setting them up.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"line-height: 18px; word-break: break-word;\">Trying to do something else? Search our <a style=\"text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">knowledge base, we have 400+ articles </a>covering many use cases, scenarios.</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 18px; word-break: break-word;\">Still haven't found what you're looking for? We really do want to learn more &amp; help you, just email us at <a style=\"text-decoration: underline;\" title=\"support@optisigns.com\" href=\"mailto:support%40optisigns.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">support@optisigns.com.</a></p>"}, {"id": 35626165056787, "url": "https://optisignshelp.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/35626165056787.json", "html_url": "https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/35626165056787-How-to-Contact-OptiSigns-Support", "author_id": 30963645258899, "comments_disabled": false, "draft": false, "promoted": false, "position": 2, "vote_sum": 2, "vote_count": 4, "section_id": 26398357451923, "created_at": "2024-11-20T21:45:25Z", "updated_at": "2025-07-03T07:16:52Z", "name": "How to Contact OptiSigns Support", "title": "How to Contact OptiSigns Support", "source_locale": "en-us", "locale": "en-us", "outdated": false, "outdated_locales": [], "edited_at": "2025-07-03T07:16:52Z", "user_segment_id": null, "permission_group_id": 787493, "content_tag_ids": [], "label_names": [], "body": "<p><strong>Email Support:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:support@optisigns.com\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-underline\" style=\"color: #1155cc;\">support@optisigns.com</span></a></p>\n<p><strong>Email Support Hours:</strong> 7AM - 7PM US CDT</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Phone Support:</strong> +1 (832) 410-8132</p>\n<p><strong>Phone Support Hours:</strong> 7AM - 7PM US CDT</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Having trouble with your screens? Try these common <a href=\"https://links.optisigns.com/pQ4C\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-underline\" style=\"color: #1155cc;\">troubleshooting steps</span></a>.</p>\n<p>Outside support hours? Submit a <a href=\"https://links.optisigns.com/new-ticket\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-underline\" style=\"color: #1155cc;\">New Ticket Request</span></a>.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Our Support team is primarily based in <strong>Houston, TX.</strong></p>\n<p>Support options are based on your<a href=\"https://www.optisigns.com/pricing\"> <span class=\"wysiwyg-underline\" style=\"color: #1155cc;\">product plan</span></a>.</p>\n<div>\n<table style=\"width: 67.1427%; height: 132px;\">\n<colgroup>\n<col>\n<col>\n<col>\n<col>\n<col>\n</colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22px; width: 18.7143%;\"> </td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 22px; width: 10.7143%;\"><strong>Email</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 22px; width: 12.2857%;\"><strong>Phone</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 22px; width: 11.2857%;\"><strong>Zoom</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 22px; width: 9.54309%;\"><strong>Dedicated Account Manager</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 22px;